@vandythepink x @asics are serving up something special 🍦 The label is bringing a Neapolitan ice cream-inspired aesthetic to the GEL-Kayano 12.1, complete with “Vanilla” and limited-edition “Chocolate” iterations.
Dropping for $195 USD, you can cop the pack early at the brand’s LA pop-up (Aug 1-2) or via VANDYTHEPINK online on August 8. A wider global release for the Vanilla colorway follows on August 14.
